title: Star Wars Battlefront 2
description:
Star Wars: Battlefront II is a first and third-person shooter video game developed by Pandemic Studios, and published by LucasArts. The game is the sequel to the successful Star Wars: Battlefront and features new vehicles, characters, game mechanics, maps, and missions.

Same as cider wrapped version except wine skinned so there is no shakiness or buggyness although load times are increased when appearing complete to about 30-40 seconds
